org.apache.streams.urls

Class LinkResolverHelperFunctions

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.streams.urls.LinkResolverHelperFunctions

  • public final class LinkResolverHelperFunctions
extends Object
    This is a static utility helper class to verify strings are URLs, obey domain sensitivity, and find URLs within a string. It cannot be, instantiated and can only be referenced through the static accessor functions
